{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Set channel outputs 1-to-1\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Written by Ben Smith - 2021\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 Info\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Routes tracks to the same output as their input, allowing quick routing for Virtual Sound Checks in live situations.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 User customisation\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab ignoreFolders = true\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab If tracks contain other tracks, the script will ignore these, rather than routing them.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab tracksToUse = all / selected\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Decides whether the script should target all tracks in the project, or only the selected tracks.\sa180\sa180\par}
}

