{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Put selected tracks in a new folder\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Written by Ben Smith - 2021\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 Info\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Indents the selected tracks and places a new folder track above them\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Useful for organising large projects quickly.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 User customisation\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab askForName = true\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Sets whether the script automatically asks for a name for the new folder, or simply adds a blank folder.\sa180\sa180\par}
